^un pain blanc // {"headword":"pain blanc","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^une pâtisserie // {"headword":"pâtisserie","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^un soda // {"headword":"soda","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"A1"}
Pain blanc, pâtisseries, sodas, etc.

^the carbohydrate // {"headword":"carbohydrate","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B1"}
%# Carbohydrates

^important // {"headword":"important","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"A1"}
?~What is the most important thing about carbohydrates?
^limit // {"headword":"limit","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^the quantity // {"headword":"quantity","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^choose // {"headword":"choose","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^well // {"headword":"well","category":"other","cefrLevel":"A1"}
Not to limit their quantity, but rather to choose them well.

^common // {"headword":"common","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"A2"}
?~What are the most common carbohydrates?
^the sugar // {"headword":"sugar","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^the starch // {"headword":"starch","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^the fibre // {"headword":"fibre","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B1"}
Sugar, starch, and fibre.

^the source // {"headword":"source","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B1"}
?~What are the sources of "good" carbohydrates?
^the whole grain // {"headword":"whole grain","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^the vegetable // {"headword":"vegetable","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^the fruit // {"headword":"fruit","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^the legume // {"headword":"legume","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B1"}
Whole grains, vegetables, fruits, legumes.

^bad // {"headword":"bad","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"A1"}
?~What are the sources of "bad" carbohydrates?
^the white bread // {"headword":"white bread","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^the pastry // {"headword":"pastry","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^the soda // {"headword":"soda","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"A2"}
White bread, pastries, sodas, etc.

^das Kohlenhydrat // {"headword":"Kohlenhydrat","category":"noun","gender":"neuter","cefrLevel":"B1"}
%# Kohlenhydrate

^wichtig // {"headword":"wichtig","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"A1"}
?~Was ist das Wichtigste über Kohlenhydrate?
^begrenzen // {"headword":"begrenzen","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B2"}
