^das Gemüse // {"headword":"Gemüse","category":"noun","gender":"neuter","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^das Obst // {"headword":"Obst","category":"noun","gender":"neuter","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^die Hülsenfrucht // {"headword":"Hülsenfrucht","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
Vollkorngetreide, Gemüse, Obst, Hülsenfrüchte.

^schlecht // {"headword":"schlecht","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"A1"}
?~Was sind die Quellen für "schlechte" Kohlenhydrate?
^das Weißbrot // {"headword":"Weißbrot","category":"noun","gender":"neuter","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^die Backware // {"headword":"Backware","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
